recommender/data/aoty_scraped/
grader/data/*
# Local-only workflow copy (tracked template optional elsewhere)
grader/discogs_release_marketplace_workflow.md
# Discogs ↔ AOTY matching HTTP cache (release→master, search JSON)
**/.discogs_cache/
artifacts/*
